<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Motivation for Students</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            overflow: hidden; /* Hide any overflow to avoid scrollbars */
            animation: backgroundAnimation 10s infinite alternate; /* Background color animation */
        }

        @keyframes backgroundAnimation {
            0% { background-color: #f8f9fa; }
            50% { background-color: #e3e8ee; }
            100% { background-color: #f8f9fa; }
        }

        #nav {
            width: 100%;
            height: 60px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            align-items: center;
            background-color: rgb(124, 124, 228);
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        #nav #eamcet {
            color: white;
            font-size: 24px;
        }
        #nav a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: white;
            font-size: 18px;
            margin: 0 10px;
        }
        
        #nav a:hover {
            border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5); 
        }
        @media(max-width: 600px) {
            #nav {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: flex-start;
                height: auto;
            }
            #nav #eamcet {
                margin-bottom: 10px;
                padding-left: 10px;
            }
            #nav a {
                margin: 5px 0;
                padding: 10px 0;
                color: white;
                padding-left: 10px;
            }
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            text-align: center;
            animation: fadeIn 2s ease-in;
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 28px;
            color: #007bff;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #555;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .quote {
            font-size: 20px;
            color: #333;
            font-style: italic;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            animation: fadeIn 3s ease-in;
            animation-delay: 1s;
            animation-fill-mode: both;
        }

        .author {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #007bff;
            margin-top: -10px;
            animation: fadeIn 3s ease-in;
            animation-delay: 1.5s;
            animation-fill-mode: both;
        }

        .footer1 {
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div id="nav">
        <h2 id="eamcet">APEAPCET 2024</h2>
        <a href="/details">Home</a>
        <a href="/top">Top Colleges</a>
        <a href="https://cets.apsche.ap.gov.in/EAPCET/PDF/APEAPCET2024_Notification_V2.pdf">Notifications</a>
        <a href="https://cets.apsche.ap.gov.in/EAPCET/EapcetHomepages/ImportantDates.aspx">Important Dates</a>
    </div>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Keep Pushing Forward</h1>
        <p>Dear Student,</p>
        <p>
            Your recent results may not have been what you hoped for, but remember that they do not define your worth or potential. Every setback is an opportunity to learn, grow, and come back stronger.
        </p>
        <p class="quote">"Success is not final, failure is not fatal: It is the courage to continue that counts."</p>
        <p class="author">- Winston S. Churchill</p>
        <p>
            Believe in yourself, keep working hard, and never give up on your dreams. Great things take time, and with perseverance, you can achieve anything you set your mind to.
        </p>
        <div class="footer1">
            <p>Best Wishes,</p>
            <p>God Bless You</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
